source.name: 2010-2017 Defense Logistics Agency Strategic Plan
source.description: The Strategic Plan focuses on incorporating three overarching goals: Warfighter Support Enhancement; Stewardship Excellence; and Workforce Development.  These three goals and their core strategies require warfighter-focused, globally responsive supply chain leadership. This is DLA's vision and pledge of support to the men and women we serve, our many mission partners, and our stakeholders.
